---
title: Diary Entries
order: 1
blurb: Long-form dive diaries — full adventures from the dives I do, start to finish.
---

Diary Entries are the heart of Diving Diaries — long-form videos that take you
along on a full dive, from the drive before dawn to the drop into the blue and
everything the ocean shows us that day.

Each entry is a numbered chapter in an ongoing log, following my journey as a
diver from my home waters on the Gold Coast to sites further afield.
